      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA168-kiḷavi">itu tōḻi yiravukkuṟi maṟuttatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante refused a night tryst.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA168">
<l>            curumpuṇa virinta karuṅkāl vēṅkaip</l>
<l>            peruñciṉai toṭutta koḻuṅka ṇiṟāaṟ</l>
<l>            puḷḷuṟṟuk kacinta tīntēṉ kallaḷaik</l>
<l>            kuṟakkuṟu mākka ḷuṇṭa miccilaip</l>
<l>            puṉṟalai manti vaṉpaṟaḻ nakku </l>
<l>            naṉmalai nāṭa paṇpeṉap paṭumō</l>
<l>            niṉṉayan tuṟaivi yiṉṉuyi ruḷḷā</l>
<l>            yaṇaṅkuṭai yaravi ṉōriru ṇaṭunāṇ</l>
<l>            maipaṭu ciṟuneṟi yeḵkutuṇai yāka</l>
<l>            vāraṅ kamaḻu mārpiṉai </l>
<l>            cāraṟ ciṟukuṭi yīṅkunī varalē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O man from a land of good mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent3">where the strong young one of the red-headed female monkey licks</l>
<l rend="indent3">the rest of what had been eaten by the youths of the forest people </l>
<l rend="indent">from a hole [made by] a stone, the sweet honey that trickled out, beloved by the bees,<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">puḷ uṟṟu: puḷ</term> in this context certainly has to be understood as bee (as is argued by T.V.G.), but how to take the <term xml:lang="ta">uṟṟu</term>? Does it simply point to the origin of the honey?</note></l>
<l rend="indent">from the large(?)<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">koḻum kaṇ</term>: "of rich area/eyes" - does this just mean large or does it refer to the openings in the honeycomb, or to its being filled?</note> honeycomb fastened to a big branch</l>
<l rend="indent2">of the dark-trunked Vēṅkai tree that spreads [flowers] for the bees to eat,</l>
<l rend="indent3">will it be called righteous,</l>
<l>– your coming here to the small hamlets on the slope,</l>
<l>you with a chest fragrant with sandal,</l>
<l>[your one] companion [your] lance on the small path suffused in</l>
<l rend="indent">dark at midnight of singular darkness, with dangerous snakes,</l>
<l>you not remembering the sweet life of her who remains longing</l>
<l rend="indent3">for you?</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
          </body>
        </text>
